text: Alfred Grosche (born 20 January 1950) is a German ski jumper. He competed at the 1972 Winter Olympics and the 1976 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:German male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of West Germany Category:Ski jumpers at the 1972 Winter Olympics Category:Ski jumpers at the 1976 Winter Olympics Category:People from Winterberg
